&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Kunai builds full-stack technology solutions for banks, credit and payment networks, infrastructure providers, and their customers. Together, we are changing the world’s relationship with financial services. At Kunai, we help our clients modernize, capitalize on emerging trends, and evolve their business for the coming decades by remaining tech-agnostic and human-centered.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;At Kunai, we’re always searching for exceptional talent to help us shape the future of digital product development. If you don’t see a role that aligns with your skills right now, this is your chance to get on our radar for future opportunities!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;By joining our Talent Community, you’ll be the first group we review when new roles open up, giving you early access to opportunities before they’re publicly posted. Whether you’re a developer, designer, strategist, or problem-solver, we want to connect with you.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Join Kunai’s Talent Community?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Be First in Line:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;You’ll be the first group we review when new roles open up, giving you a head start on joining the Kunai team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Find Your Fit:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;We’ll match your skills and passions with the right opportunities as they arise.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thrive with Us:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Enjoy a supportive environment where your contributions are valued and your growth is prioritized.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Shape the Future:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Be part of a team that’s transforming industries and delivering impactful solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Passionate individuals who excel in dynamic, fast-paced environments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Problem-solvers who are eager to learn and make a meaningful impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Team-oriented professionals who value diversity and shared success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re excited about the possibility of working at Kunai but don’t see the perfect role today, apply here and let’s start the conversation. Your future at Kunai could be just around the corner!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our success over the past 20 years is rooted in our exceptional team, which thrives in a culture of collaboration, creativity, and continuous learning.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;We are proud to offer our employees a range of benefits, including competitive compensation, professional development opportunities, and flexible work arrangements, all designed to help them thrive. As we continue to expand, we remain committed to cultivating an environment where people feel valued, have a voice, and are given the tools to grow—both personally and professionally—while pushing the boundaries of innovation in the fintech industry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;Minimum Degree Required:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Bachelor’s Degree, in lieu of a degree, demonstrating in addition to the minimum years of experience required for the role, three years of specialized training and/or progressively responsible work experience in technology for each missing year of college is&amp;nbsp;required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

